---
title: Seared Steak & Mumbai Coconut Sauce with Bombay Potatoes & Garden Salad
description: We can't work out which is best: the pop of brown mustard seeds on the turmeric-roasted potatoes, the gentle warmth of the creamy Mumbai-spiced coconut sauce or the burst and crunch of the garden salad. You decide!
